## Icon

> Our mission is to make affordable, ecological housing accessible to everyone. 
> The OBI system is open source, collaborative and distributed. Our focus is on low cost and rapidly-built structures that are modular, ecological, and energy efficient.

[https://www.openbuildinginstitute.org/](https://www.openbuildinginstitute.org/ "https://www.openbuildinginstitute.org/")

